    q = int(input())

        for j in range(l-1, r):
            a[j] += x
    b = [0]*n
    c = [0]*n
    for i in range(n):
        b[i] = max(b[i-1], a[i])
        c[i] = max(c[i-1], a[i])

        c[r-1] += x
        for j in range(l-1, r):
            b[j] += x
            c[j] += x
        b[l-1] = max(b[l-1], b[l-2])
        c[r-1] = max(c[r-1], c[r-2])
        for j in range(l-1, r):
            b[j] = max(b[j], b[j-1])
            c[j] = max(c[j], c[j-1])

n = int(input())
    s = input()
    r = 0
    b = 0
    max_r = 0
    max_b = 0
    max_r_start = 0
    max_b_start = 0
    for i in range(n):
        if s[i] == 'R':
            r += 1
        else:
            b += 1
        if r - b > max_r:
            max_r = r - b
            max_r_start = i + 1
        if b - r > max_b:
            max_b = b - r
            max_b_start = i + 1
    print(max_r_start, max_b_start)

n, m = map(int, input().split())
    friends = [[] for i in range(n)]
    for i in range(m):
        u, v = map(int, input().split())
        friends[u-1].append(v-1)
        friends[v-1].append(u-1)
    for i in range(n):
        friends[i].sort()
    steps = 0
    selected = [0]
    while len(selected) < n:
        selected.append(friends[selected[-1]][0])
        for i in range(len(friends[selected[-1]])):
            if friends[selected[-1]][i] not in selected:
                friends[selected[-1]][i] = -1
        friends[selected[-1]] = []
        steps += 1
    print(steps)
    print(*selected)
